data.description: One or more photo(s) have been virtually staged. Welcome to this beautiful 3 bed/2 bath home in the desirable Silver Oaks Community in Apopka! This spacious one-story single-family home has over 1,900 sq. feet of living space. The kitchen boasts stainless steel appliances, designer 42-inch cabinets, and an oversized island with room for barstools that overlooks the family room. The split floor plan has two bedrooms in the front and the owner’s suite towards the rear of the home. The owner’s suite is big enough to comfortably fit a king-size bed and has a huge walk-in closet with an en suite offering a double vanity and walk-in shower. The two-car garage gives you plenty of room for parking. This quiet community also offers a community pool, park, and playground. Conveniently located – just minutes from the 414 Maitland Blvd Extension, 429 Beltway, Downtown Apopka, AdventHealth Apopka, Wekiva Springs, plenty of shopping plazas, restaurants, entertainment, and so much more! Come see it for yourself today!
